  "title": "Strictly Decreasing Sequence",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $(x_n)$ be a real sequence. The sequence $(x_n)$ is\n\\textbf{strictly decreasing} if\n\\[\n x_{n+1} < x_n\n \\qquad\n \\text{for every } n\\in\\mathbb{N}.\n\\]",
